reviewText: This Scooby Doo vhs has 2 episodes on it. A clue for scooby doo and hassle in the castle. They did a great job making this tape because it is its originality. The theme song is in its original way and they didn't change up any of the episode airing. 5 stars.

our whole family loves scoody doo and we are trying to get all the dvds made of him...this is such a neat dvd and the cats love him too.  thanks
We like Scooby Doo, so we liked this also. 8 yr.old Granddaughter really likes this. Only 2 episodes on it. Is great for when you have a short time to watch,or someone with a short attention span.

We got this dvd for Christmas; my 3 year old loves it!  I thought he would be too young to appreciate it, but he's hooked.  We watched it two times today.  This is the orignal Scooby, which aired in the 60's.  A real classic!
